15.text: A Day in the Life of a News Reader

16.text: What is the life of a news reader like? To say the least, it’s hectic. I always work with tight deadlines, but I love the challenge it provides.I meet so many interesting people every day. I start my day at 7.00 in the morning and work till about 10.00 in the night. Most of the time, I am expected to be well dressed. Of all the work I do, breaking news is the most exciting time in my job; I get no breaks during breaking news.
